node.text:
What makes a great "circuit breaker" day 31 burger?  Wagyu beef patty, lettuce, bacon, halloumi, tomato and a dirty-diner fried runny-yolk egg piled high in between a pan grilled mini butter bun... All washed down with a Grapefruit Tiger Radler... Tummy is full and feeling grateful for the daily food on the table... 😋❤️
